<div class="span10">
  <h2>Tanda Terima</h2>
  <hr/>
  <p>Pada hari ini, tanggal <%= Time.now.strftime("%d %B %Y")%>, telah diterima pemasukan data dan upload file calon mahasiswa dengan data sebagai berikut:</p>
  <br/>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span2">Nama</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.full_name%></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span2">Alamat</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.address%></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span2">Program Studi</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.to_program%></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span2">Email</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.email%></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span2">No. Peserta</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.number%></div>
  </div>
  <br/>
  <p>Selanjutnya dipersilahkan untuk membayar sejumlah <%="#{number_to_currency(@candidate.number.to_s[4,7].to_i + 500000, :unit => 'Rp.')}"%> ke Rekening Bank Mandiri a.n YPT/ITTelkom 7330180123.</p>
  <br/>
  <hr/>
  <h2>Tanda Bukti Hadir Tes Tulis</h2>
  <hr/>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span2">
      <%= image_tag(@candidate.photo.url(:medium), :size => "200x200")%>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span2">Nama</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.full_name%></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span2">No. Peserta</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.number%></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span2">No. Telp</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.phone%></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span2">Email</div><div class="span2">: <%= @candidate.email%></div>
      </div>
      <br/>
      <p>Tanda tangan dilakukan <b>PADA SAAT TES TERTULIS</b>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br/>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
      <p>Pengawas</p>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <p>(________________________________)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <p>Peserta</p>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <p>(________________________________)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>